            <td style="line-height: 19px;" valign="top"><p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="4"><strong>2012, Terrorism,  Iraq, Afghanistan and much more.&nbsp; The  common factor with all these matters?&nbsp;  Military Implication and Military Hardware at work.</strong></font></p>
              <p><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Aura Systems Inc.  (AUSI) a technology company headquartered in El Segundo, assembles and sells  the AuraGen/VIPER (VIPER is the name used by the US Military), their patented,  integrated, mobile power generator and power management system that installs in  a motor vehicle and delivers on-location, both AC and DC electricity for any  end user including industrial, commercial, recreational and military  applications.&nbsp; AURA Systems Inc., has  made a business out of supporting the troops and all their hardware.&nbsp; In an economy where profit is the driving  force, AURA Systems Inc. has gone back to the basics and is making sure that  the troops will always have the power and energy needed to support all other  troops and push forth the effort required in making the world a better and  safer place.</font></p>
              <p><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><a href="http://wall-street-stock.net/go.php/637316/345544778/4233012"><img src="http://images.wall-street-stock.net/img/x/xplosivestocks/001/aura-logo.jpg" align="right" border="0" vspace="5" width="268" height="80" hspace="5"></a>Oil will come and go,  the planet is filled with gold and other valuable resources, but energy is a  necessity which we can never do without!&nbsp;  Aura Systems has made energy available to all in portable, mobile  platform.&nbsp; Consider it, Energy on the Go!</font></p>
              <p><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">AURA is in a market with annual sales  of well over 1 Trillion US Dollars.&nbsp; The  Military Supplies and Arms market is a growing market as every nation seeks to protect  themselves and their citizens.&nbsp; Military  expenses and budgets are constantly on the rise and AURA Systems Inc. is  fortunate to have begun to tap into the Military Supplies Market at an international  level.&nbsp; In the United States alone, the  potential market for AURA Systems Inc. Viper Generators is $600 Million Dollars  a Year.&nbsp; On a worldwide scale, both for  Military and Commercial applications, it can be easily estimated that AURA  Systems Inc. will be tapping into a Trillion Dollar sales stream.&nbsp; AURA Systems Inc., stands at the crossroads  of the Energy and Military Industries, two of the world&#8217;s biggest ongoing  markets.&nbsp; While the military applications  of AURA Systems Inc. Viper product have been recognized the world over, let us  not forget their commercial offering the AuraGen system has caught the  attention of such major clients as Kraft Foods and other various industry  giants.</font></p>
              <font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">At  current levels, Aura Systems Inc. is still a bargain.&nbsp; As it taps into the growing Military Supplies  and Energy market, Aura Systems only stands to return greater numbers for  investors.&nbsp; In our opinion this is a  company well deserved of being traded in the Dollar Range. </font></td>
